        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(security): enforce private directory mode 0o700 for managed state dirs",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\n`mkdirSync({recursive: true})` without explicit `mode` inherits umask-derived permissions (775/755 instead of 700). This exposes session transcripts, tool binaries, plugin skills, and settings directories under `~/.openclaw` to group/other users on multi-user systems.\n\nFixes #92771\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nThe project already has ~10 locations that correctly use `mode: 0o700`. However, 12 `mkdirSync` calls in session lifecycle and agent infrastructure did not enforce private permissions. This PR:\n- Adds `mode: 0o700` to managed OpenClaw state dir creation (NOT custom/user-configured paths)\n- Adds best-effort `chmodSync` repair for **existing** dirs after upgrade (session-manager, settings-manager, tools-manager, plugin-skills)\n- Preserves caller-owned custom paths (`session.store`, export targets) — no forced mode\n\n## User Impact\n\n- All managed directories under `~/.openclaw` now consistently created with owner-only permissions (0700)\n- **Existing** permissive dirs are repaired on next agent startup (chmod in getDefaultSessionDir, settings-manager, tools-manager, plugin-skills)\n- Custom `session.store` paths unchanged\n- No config changes required\n\n## Evidence\n\n### Fresh install (umask 0002)\n```\n修复前：agents/ → 775 ❌  sessions/ → 775 ❌  plugin-skills/ → 775 ❌\n修复后：agents/ → 700 ✅  sessions/ → 700 ✅  plugin-skills/ → 700 ✅\n```\n\n### Upgrade repair (pre-existing 775 dirs)\nAfter amendment (ef1adecec5): chmodSync repair added to `getDefaultSessionDir`, `settings-manager.withLock`, `tools-manager`, `plugin-skills`. Existing 775 dirs are repaired to 700 on next access — no manual migration needed.\n\n### Custom path preservation\n- `store.ts:858` (`saveSessionStoreUnlocked`): reverted — respects caller-configured `session.store` paths\n- `json-files.ts:105` (`writeTextAtomic`): reverted — `dirMode` default unchanged, avoids broad compatibility impact\n\n### Screenshots\n| Before fix | After fix |\n|---|---|\n| ![reproduction](reproduction-evidence) | ![fix-verified](fix-verified) |\n\n### Tests\n- `src/config/sessions/sessions.test.ts` — 46 tests ✅\n- `src/config/sessions/paths.test.ts` — 16 tests ✅\n- Build ✅\n\n| Files changed | +/− |\n|---|---|\n| 9 files | +40 / −14 |\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)",
